headline: What will Google Search remedies mean for online travel?
summary: Investing.com -- U.S. District Judge Amit Mehta’s ruling in the Google (NASDAQ:GOOGL) Search antitrust case is set to reshape online travel by curbing Google’s ability to secure exclusive search agreements.

headline: New York’s Airbnb Crackdown, in Force for Two Years, Hasn’t Improved Housing Supply
summary: It is harder than ever to find an apartment in NYC two years after the city cracked down on illegal Airbnb units and other short-term rentals.
